      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "APILLA (1) has a strong record this trip with 11 wins and six placings from 22 starts. Comes off a (42.41) win last time, scoring by 17 lengths in a Grade 3/4/5 over 730m at this track. Looks a key chance on best form. MOSCOW CHICK (7) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 1.75 lengths back in third (34.46) at this track in a Other over 595m. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can feature again. NITRO NEO (5) ran a good time (43.96) when placing three back at this track but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing fifth (44.24) at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. WEBLEC POLLY (3) is in the mix after placing in good time last start.",
